{"tid":1154362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受惠通俄門報告經濟數據佳　特朗普支持度升至46%任內新高","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:41:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab01e9388eeb5b6f03ce977b9427ef4155e63d6e","tid":1154362,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"受惠通俄門報告經濟數據佳 特朗普支持度升至46%任內新高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190507/s00005/1557205063756/%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BD%B3-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%BA%A6%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B346-%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A7%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00005%2F1557205063756%2F%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2583%25A0%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2587%25B346-%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ef4fb49c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00005%2F1557205063756%2F%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2583%25A0%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2587%25B346-%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&h=009cc6c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190507/s00005/1557205063756/%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BD%B3-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%BA%A6%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B346-%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A7%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98</a><br />\n<br />\n民調機構蓋洛普（Gallup）公布最新調查結果顯示，在特別檢察官米勒（Robert Mueller）的「通俄門」調查報告發布後，加上經濟數據正面，美國總統特朗普的支持度升至46%上任以來新高。<br />\n<br />\n民調結果指出，截至4月30日前的兩星期，特朗普的施政滿意度達46%，較前一次調查上升1個百分點。和3月初的39%相比，實質上升。<br />\n<br />\n蓋洛普分析，米勒調查報告最初的解讀，令特朗普可以聲稱還了自己清白，洗脫他與俄羅斯勾結的罪名。而經濟表現強亦令更多國民認同特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民調數據亦顯示，特朗普的表現仍未合格，儘管已經從3月10日的57%下降7個百分點，他的不滿意度仍高達50%。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）"},{"pid":"4f31db681c4ff791266e53fef191de84ff737505","tid":1154362,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5e931764d951d648f832455bcd42bcd5067016","tid":1154362,"uid":174498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"所有民調唔撚準 等中期選舉啦屌"},{"pid":"26b06e00d1411b7ff34c8b406722093b0579b8ee","tid":1154362,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"In侵 we trust"},{"pid":"357a20cee18ebae40757f3dd4481e578cdba840d","tid":1154362,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}